            "title_desktopl": "What You See Is What You Get"
          }
        },
        "0225bb6a-d5fc-48bc-902d-c6a41e175014": {
          "type": "contents_desktopl",
          "settings": {
            "linked_iddl": "tab1",
            "content_dl": "<p>Managing metabolic disorders can be a challenging and overwhelming experience and can have a significant impact on your quality of life. When you’re able to get your conditions under control, however, the benefits are immeasurable! You'll experience improvements in physical health, like better blood sugar control and lower blood pressure, and a boost in mental and emotional well-being. Plus, with all that extra energy, you'll be able to take on the world and enjoy life to the fullest!<\/p>",
            "image_dl": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/science-page-start-img-1.png"
          }
        },
        "7b4768ae-f01a-418e-a416-a10bec8645b1": {
          "type": "contents_desktopl",
          "settings": {
            "linked_iddl": "tab2",
            "content_dl": "<p>We believe in the power of nature and ancient knowledge to provide healing and wellness. We are constantly exploring the natural world for potent ingredients and incorporating ancient techniques and remedies into our products and formulations. While some of the scientific terms and concepts may be unfamiliar to some, we trust in the expertise and research from our team to bring you the most effective and natural solutions possible.<\/p>",
            "image_dl": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/science-page-start-img-2.png"
          }
        },
        "55e48920-6cc9-4810-a79e-f668e6f97182": {
          "type": "contents_desktopl",
          "settings": {
            "linked_iddl": "tab3",
            "content_dl": "<p>There are no hidden secrets or surprises in our formulas - what you see is exactly what you get. We prioritize transparency so you can feel confident and comfortable with what you're putting into your body. We're proud to offer ingredients that are clinically tested, non-GMO, vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-free, so you can feel at ease.<\/p>",
            "image_dl": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/science-page-start-img-3.png"
          }
        },
        "c5ef775b-aee8-49bd-ade2-ae610a827729": {
          "type": "contents_desktopl",
          "settings": {
            "linked_iddl": "tab4",
            "content_dl": "<p>We take pride in the quality and safety of our products. Our products are manufactured in facilities that meet the highest requirements for transparency and traceability and have been regulated by the FDA and certified by third parties to be in compliance with current Good Manufacturing Practices (cGMPs). Each capsule is carefully formulated to meet our specifications for purity, and potency, and is rigorously tested to ensure that it meets all label claims and free from contaminants. We prioritize the quality and safety of our products, and are committed to providing our customers with the best possible health and wellness solutions.<\/p>",
            "image_dl": "shopify:\/\/shop_images\/science-page-start-img-4.png"
          }
        },
